OL,3,CCommons Speaker Sir Lindsay Hoyle
OL,4,Cunder pressure - what happens next?
OL,6,FHis decision sparked fury from the
OL,7,FConservative and SNP benches, some of
OL,8,Fwhom stormed out of the chamber and
OL,9,Faccused him of helping Sir Keir
OL,10,FStarmer avoid another damaging revolt.
OL,12,FSir Lindsay issued an apology after a
OL,13,Fday of acrimony but continues to face
OL,14,Fcalls to resign.
OL,16,FSo, what exactly is Sir Lindsay's role
OL,17,Fand could he be sacked? ITV News
OL,18,Fexplains.
OL,20,FWhat is the Speaker of the House of
OL,21,FCommons?
