OL,3,CCommons Speaker Sir Lindsay Hoyle
OL,4,Cunder pressure - what happens next?
OL,6,FMore than 50 MPs signed a
OL,7,Fparliamentary motion tabled by a Tory
OL,8,FMP declaring no confidence in Sir
OL,9,FLindsay Hoyle following the chaos in
OL,10,Fthe chamber on Wednesday.
OL,12,FThe motion was presented as an early-
OL,13,Fday motion (EDM), which is a way for
OL,14,FMPs to express their views and draw
OL,15,Fattention to specific events or
OL,16,Fcampaigns.
OL,18,FEDMs are rarely debated but they can
OL,19,Fgenerate huge amounts of public
OL,20,Finterest and media coverage depending
OL,21,Fon the issue.
