OL,3,CCommons Speaker Sir Lindsay Hoyle
OL,4,Cunder pressure - what happens next?
OL,6,FSNP and Conservative party members
OL,7,Fcame together in criticism of Sir
OL,8,FLindsay on Wednesday, and have
OL,9,Fcontinued to express their unhappiness
OL,10,Fin discussion in the chamber and in
OL,11,Fmedia interviews on Thursday.
OL,13,FSNP Westminster leader Stephen Flynn
OL,14,Fhas called for a no-confidence vote in
OL,15,Fthe Speaker, while Scottish
OL,16,FConservative leader Douglas Ross said
OL,17,Ftrust in Sir Lindsay has been "eroded"
OL,18,Fafter the events of Wednesday evening.
