OL,3,CCommons Speaker Sir Lindsay Hoyle
OL,4,Cunder pressure - what happens next?
OL,6,FSNP Leader Humza Yousaf said Sir
OL,7,FLindsay's position appeared untenable
OL,8,Fand suggested that he had "bent the
OL,9,Frules".
OL,11,FCommons Leader Penny Mordaunt and Tory
OL,12,FChief Whip Simon Hart would have to
OL,13,Fgrant parliamentary time for a no-
OL,14,Fconfidence vote to take place.
OL,16,FAn overwhelming majority in a no-
OL,17,Fconfidence vote would typically prompt
OL,18,Fa government official to resign.
OL,20,FHow would a new Speaker be chosen?
